lling air quality now.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 12pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">You have stumbled into this with this rather naive report that generated very naive headlines. I think it would have been better for the protection of my constituents and people like them in other parts of the north-west if we had had a proper consideration of what it is like if you drop this toxic soup that my colleague has just referred to into an area that already has appallingly poor quality.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 14.2pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">Duncan </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">Selbie</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">: We have not stumbled into this at all, but we do share your concern. It is our first responsibility to make sure that people are not exposed to these chemicals. It is our first responsibility to make sure—</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold">Q39 </span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Barbara </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Keeley</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">:</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt"> So </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">what</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt"> will you do?</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 14.2pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">Duncan </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; f