lth profiles, which are fabulous, on every local authority in the land. In four pages, they tell you everything you could ever want to know about what is happening.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold">Q97 </span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Valerie </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Vaz</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">:</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt"> What is your time line for creating it? When are you going to do it?</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 14.2pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">Duncan </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">Selbie</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">: This is happening now.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold">Q98 </span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Valerie </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Vaz</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">:</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt"> But you said </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">you</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt"> were creating something.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 14.2pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-styl